{"tid":2165723,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"!!口罩代購黑店!!唔排除已有過百名受傷者","createTime":"2020-08-20T04:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T09:41:49.000Z","uid":234220,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"114954e9854a01f156106ae55ae23cdd7169f282","tid":2165723,"uid":234220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"大家唔該要小心Instagram <strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">@korea.mask.byggf_hk </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>事法經過</ins><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">係7月頭同上面呢條仆街預購咗一盒黑色中衛口罩<br />\n ( 真係屎忽痕好想要買盒黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n當日就過咗數仲好快手咁比埋SF單number比我，仲聲稱預7月尾左右到。<br />\n到7月尾8月頭我見沒咩消息就問多佢一次，呢友都有覆我既話要delay到8月中左右。<br />\n到前兩日終於收到貨，但裡面只有一包不明來歷made in China口罩，起初我仲以為係條友唔小心出錯貨，Indox問返佢就話同供應商跟進中，最後仲潛埋水</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPXtvow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPXtvow.jpg&h=d2d4f038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">之後係苦主group發現原來好多咗人都中咗招，仲要係由3月開始到依家都已經用緊同一個手法呃人，所以受害者分分鐘已經過百人，依家呢友仲做埋台灣食品代購亦都唔排除佢可能再有其他分身，所以大家過數之前看清楚下面有無一款資料係一樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">黑店資料</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Instagram A/C: korea.mask.byggf_hk<br />\n後備A/C: <a href=\"http://korea.mask.byggf_.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkorea.mask.byggf_.hk&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=9f5b7bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">korea.mask.byggf_.hk</a><br />\n條友之前不斷改名，所以要小心korea mask 開頭</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3H5xB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3H5xB5.jpg&h=7cfcfdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPAScMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPAScMu.jpg&h=1150806e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qMRtkK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qMRtkK.jpg&h=bab52800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">Account number: 恆生# 204653166668 CHAN N** C****<br />\nPAYME Code: Stephen Chan / SC </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkGh8p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkGh8p1.jpg&h=db89dd35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">GIGI FONG <br />\n地址:  將軍澳田下灣村18號2樓<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijj7Mcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fijj7Mcx.jpg&h=f1b2196b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經報咗海關同消費者委員會，開PO唔係話想追返啲錢，百幾蚊自己當買咗個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，只係為咗唔想再增加受害者既數目，同一開始都諗唔到條友原來已經呃咗咁多人，希望大家注意一下!"},{"pid":"1319c79e1ae4909ee03dd57ebdc02db58c34679c","tid":2165723,"uid":241764,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"IG Shop<br />\n買口罩<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7996e4a076e8d252c8760c86f6f62c49aa29c0","tid":2165723,"uid":188907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"中衛黑色 街有現貨<br />\n貴少少但唔洗等<br />\n<br />\n上網買始終太多騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4c25a7bd1cd486fccabd58635c5dd9feaa8114","tid":2165723,"uid":234220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7996e4a076e8d252c8760c86f6f62c49aa29c0","tid":2165723,"uid":188907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"中衛黑色 街有現貨<br />\n貴少少但唔洗等<br />\n<br />\n上網買始終太多騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"係邊度見到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /